{"tid":1101804,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"無良偽慈善專頁，偷偷帶狗仔八哥去人道毀滅","createTime":"2019-04-11T09:29:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-13T14:33:44.000Z","uid":163252,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2e492a4fe6ee253767c7951efabe89dcae1b34d5","tid":1101804,"uid":163252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T09:29:49.000Z","msg":"專頁名稱：鼠鼠之家　hkvxv<br />\n<br />\n事源：本身有個主人醫自己隻有狗瘟的八哥醫到無能力照顧（棄養正仆街）？跟住想交佢比慈善組織收養，想佢地可以好好照顧八哥。點知果位所謂既義工係facebook page鼠鼠之家既群主，佢明明只係接受鼠，點知連狗都收。最後講大話扮帶八哥去睇醫生，跟住話佢死左仲要火化埋。網友叫佢出示醫藥單同火化證明，佢全部都無，仲要講大話加潛水。實質係人道人道毀滅。然後接二連三有唔少動物義工爆左（鼠鼠之家）個page主既黑幕，利用動物去賺錢，非法收錢寄養同埋葬。個page主每次去接受小動物都係帶口罩，極度可疑。無人見過所謂既創辦人Anna，每次都係果位口罩男出現。求巴打門幫手起底 大家小心（鼠鼠之家）呢個專頁 唔好害左小動物。<br />\n<br />\n事件來源：發文到 八哥大聯盟 Pug<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nWbFNDH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnWbFNDH.jpg&h=65e0c223&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n另外有人整左片上youtube<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lNWiGlW9TOM&amp;t=505s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DlNWiGlW9TOM%26t%3D505s&d=KS%2FaBsiOfKbE8rejl7UGUmWzMblEAwKPRhfqpO9yGDY%3D&h=c88b4b40\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lNWiGlW9TOM&amp;t=505s</a>"},{"pid":"311461fb39dacc5d2bc610c636284bee77f018bf","tid":1101804,"uid":163252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T09:31:42.000Z","msg":"原來條友仲假冒愛協<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"955085419639c420455da0627a14305093944273","tid":1101804,"uid":57488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T09:39:39.000Z","msg":"會唔會拎返屋企虐待動<br />\n或者轉頭又賣咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3049920ccbae543df3cf80519d47358298dbf063","tid":1101804,"uid":163252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"955085419639c420455da0627a14305093944273","tid"